                     <interp inst="t18320906-276-person2284" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at Hoxton, and am a pawnbroker. I have the trousers, which were pawned by the prisoner on the 21st of July, and on the 28th he came and had another shilling on them; he gave his own name and address.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320906-276-person2285">
                  WILLIAM 
                  EPPS
               <interp inst="t18320906-276-person2285" type="surname" value="EPPS"></interp>
