                     <interp inst="t18320906-276-person2287" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . It is false; I provided him with clothes as well as I could; I work as a carpenter; he was employed at the saw-mills, but was discharged for getting drunk and keeping bad company; he got all my things almost.</p>
